2016年2月18日，[[土耳其|土耳其]][[迪亚巴克尔省|迪亚巴克尔省]][[迪亚巴克尔|迪亚巴克尔]]发生爆炸。爆炸由一枚路边炸弹引起，造成6名士兵死亡，另有一名士兵受伤。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aa.com.tr/en/turkey/pkk-targets-military-vehicle-in-se-turkey/523291 |title=PKK targets military vehicle in SE Turkey |publisher=Aa.com.tr |date= |accessdate=2016-02-18 |archive-date=2016-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219093351/http://aa.com.tr/en/turkey/pkk-targets-military-vehicle-in-se-turkey/523291 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/02/18/middleeast/turkey-airstrikes/index.html|title=Ankara bombing aftermath: Turkish soldiers killed in new blast|author=Zeynep Bilginsoy, Joshua Berlinger and Tim Hume, CNN|date=2016-02-18|work=CNN|accessdate=2016-09-19|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114170345/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/02/18/middleeast/turkey-airstrikes/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailysabah.com/nation/2016/02/18/bus-carrying-turkish-soldiers-targeted-in-southeastern-diyarbakir-some-wounded |title=PKK attack targeting military convoy kills 6 soldiers in southeastern Diyarbakır province |publisher=沙巴日报 |date= |accessdate=2016-02-18 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912074919/https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/2016/02/18/pkk-attack-targeting-military-convoy-kills-6-soldiers-in-southeastern-diyarbakir-province |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=路透社编辑 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-blast-diyarbakir-idUSKCN0VR0T4 |title=Explosion hits military convoy in southeast Turkey, some wounded: sources |publisher=路透社 |date= |accessdate=2016-02-18 |archive-date=2016-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223103407/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-blast-diyarbakir-idUSKCN0VR0T4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rt.com/news/332845-turkey-military-convoy-blast/ |title=7 dead, many injured as blast hits military convoy in southeast Turkey – reports — RT News |publisher=今日俄罗斯网站 |date=2016-02-12 |accessdate=2016-02-18 |archive-date=2016-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219101402/https://www.rt.com/news/332845-turkey-military-convoy-blast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Constanze Letsch and agencies |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/feb/18/explosion-hits-another-turkish-military-convoy-one-day-after-ankara-attack |title=Explosion hits another Turkish military convoy one day after Ankara attack | World news |publisher=卫报 |date=2016-02-18 |accessdate=2016-02-18 |archive-date=2016-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160218132645/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/feb/18/explosion-hits-another-turkish-military-convoy-one-day-after-ankara-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2016/02/18/world/middleeast/18reuters-turkey-blast-diyarbakir-casualties.html|title=Six Soldiers Killed in Southeast Turkey Bomb Attack: Military|date=2016-02-18|work=路透社|via=纽约时报}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.todayszaman.com/national_explosion-hits-military-convoy-in-southeast-turkey_412631.html |title=6 soldiers killed in southeast Turkey bomb attack |publisher=Todayszaman.com |date= |accessdate=2016-02-18 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

